  "instructions": [
    "heat the coconut oil in a bain-marie over low heat.",
    "add the onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the garlic and ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "add the arborio rice and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "add the vegetable broth, 1/2 cup at a time, stirring constantly and allowing each portion to absorb before adding the next.",
    "after 20 minutes, stir in the coconut milk and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "add the chicken breast and cook until heated through.",
    "season with fish sauce, salt, and pepper to taste.",
    "garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
